title: DAZ3D ~ Poser : Autumn Picnic [DAZ3D 17329]
description:
--- Previously uploaded by me to KAT ---

Let the cool air roll in with this quiet little autumn set that's full of detailed foliage. The Autumn Picnic Pack has just the right amount of props for a quick and easy starter scene. It is portrayed here as a contemporary setup, but the versatility of this design means it can be used for a variety of themes.

Note: The background used in the promo renders is for demonstration purposes only and is not distributed with this pack.
